#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/floordiv.md:4
msgid "简介：取整除法，返回向零取整后的除法结果，四则运算 ‘//’，无tl.floordiv方法"
msgstr "Introduction: Floor division, returns the result of division rounded towards zero, arithmetic operator '//', no tl.floordiv method."

