#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/floordiv.md:24
msgid "### 2.3 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.3 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/floordiv.md:26
msgid "以下示例实现了对输入张量 `in_ptr0, in_ptr1` 做整除计算："
msgstr "The following example implements integer division on input tensors `in_ptr0, in_ptr1`:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/floordiv.md:28
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def triton_kernel(out_ptr0, in_ptr0, in_ptr1, N: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    idx = tl.arange(0, N)\n"
"    x = tl.load(in_ptr0 + idx)\n"
"    y = tl.load(in_ptr1 + idx)\n"
"    ret = x // y\n"
"    tl.store(out_ptr0 + idx, ret)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Math_Ops/floordiv.md:30
msgid "### 2.4. 特殊限制"
msgstr "### 2.4. Special Restrictions"

